SUMMARY:Kiana Easter Brunch & Egg Hunt
DTSTAMP:20260327T045204Z
DTSTART:20260405T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:Kiana Lodge Easter Buffet & Egg Hunt Sun April 5th\, 2026 Brunc
	h Buffet 11:00AM - 02:00PM\,Easter Bunny & Egg Hunt 12:00PM Come visit wit
	h the Easter bunny and enjoy a tasty Easter brunch at Kiana Lodge. Kids ar
	e encouraged to bring their own basket so they can find the hidden eggs fi
	lled with goodies! Adults: $54.60\, Children 5-12: $21.84\, 5 and Under: $
	5.46 Beverages: Cash Bar with Mimosa & Bloody Mary Specials Highchairs ava
